Feross Aboukhadijeh | GitHub Stars
I'm the author of open source software with 100+ million downloads per month, including WebTorrent <https://webtorrent.io> and Standard <https://standardjs.com>. I love to build things that make people say "Whoa... I didn't know that was possible!". In the past, I was on the Node.js Foundation Board of Directors and I'm heavily invested in the JavaScript, Web, and Node.js communities. Just for fun, I once ran an impromptu JavaScript conference in Svalbard, the nothern-most human settlement on Earth, with some amazing friends. I'm currently running the Speakeasy JS meetup <https://speakeasyjs.com>.
